					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7062035#post-3918565</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7062035/scp-4545#post-3918565</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 20 Aug 2018 09:01:22 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mortos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1705184</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Like most of my ideas, this came from a random throw-away comment in chat (about trojan horses, obviously) so I decided to see if I can make the concept work as an SCP. Hopefully I succeeded! Also, I was super happy when I found the image for this under creative commons!</p> <p>Thanks to CaptainKirby, Taffeta, Dora, stairfallinstitute, and cabbage for reading the draft of this!</p> <p>Image source - <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Replica_of_Trojan_Horse_-_Canakkale_Waterfront_-_Dardanelles_-_Turkey_(5747677790).jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Replica_of_Trojan_Horse_-_Canakkale_Waterfront_-_Dardanelles_-_Turkey_(5747677790).jpg</a></p> <p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/mortos-author-page" target="_blank">Check out my other stuff here!</a></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
